{"tid":2361680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮：川普週二將訪德州邊境  「視察圍牆」","createTime":"2021-01-11T01:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3fbaa1c35467ceb7b4a701bf516cea186f2bc9","tid":2361680,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/12/Trump-boards-Air-Force-One-e1607884676699-700x420-450x270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FTrump-boards-Air-Force-One-e1607884676699-700x420-450x270.jpg&h=651ed648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n (Brendan Smialowski/AFP via Getty Images)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白宮週六（1月9日）表示，川普（特朗普）總統下週二將訪問德克薩斯州，以審查美墨邊界牆建設的進展。這是他2016年競選承諾的一個重點。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》報導，川普將搭乘空軍一號於週二抵達德克薩斯州哈林根（Harlingen）。除了這一信息外，白宮新聞稿沒有提供其它細節。<br />\n<br />\n美國海關與邊境保護局（CBP）局長馬克‧摩根（Mark Morgan）週六發推文說450英里邊界牆已完工，隨後白宮公布了川普的這一日程安排。<br />\n<br />\n摩根在週六的一則推文帖子中說：「他們說我們永遠不會完成，但是我們做到了。」「說地面上豎立了450英里的鋼鐵和混凝土牆是項了不起的成就，那是輕描淡寫了。」他強調，「由於有了邊界牆系統，我們的邊界更加安全。」<br />\n<br />\n根據海關與邊境保護局截至1月6日的數據，這個邊界牆系統使用了679,000噸鋼，相當於11個紐約帝國大廈的鋼材耗量，並使用了970,000立方碼的混凝土，相當於2.2個五角大樓的混凝土耗量。<br />\n<br />\n本月早些時候，摩根在一個新聞發布會上宣布，川普政府希望在1月19日川普離開白宮前一天，以及國會認證的當選總統拜登進入白宮之前，敲定建設300英里新邊界牆的新合同。<br />\n<br />\n根據海關與邊境保護局的說法，自2017年1月以來，至少365英里的邊界牆取代了已損壞或設計過時的主要或次要圍欄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/1/10/n12679595.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F1%2F10%2Fn12679595.htm&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=e7ac9abf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/1/10/n12679595.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b2516a28a1cba1244b49f2ff329b2247e573de9b","tid":2361680,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:43:48.000Z","msg":"終於有侵既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4bcfc1aff1109192e2f0dfe5d84fa39569ad16","tid":2361680,"uid":235665,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"拜登上任就拆牆泄憤。"},{"pid":"6417c3ea2ca395a10dbde258fc1a58de51c3180c","tid":2361680,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec94ad9107d090c58aa6ff1604e2af8bf7929e4c","tid":2361680,"uid":48026,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3b4bcfc1aff1109192e2f0dfe5d84fa39569ad16","tid":2361680,"uid":235665,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"拜登上任就拆牆泄憤。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EX-KnazWAAAZZ3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEX-KnazWAAAZZ3q.jpg&h=f09aca85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38b3929ecff66b6a39be8752e8e70dc7031cdefc","tid":2361680,"uid":297997,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"好撚型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAMR8E8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAMR8E8.gif&h=05acbe21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bc0a577fd8b1324096a077be00a0e405a07a6bb","tid":2361680,"uid":186388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"引人去暗殺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde27ff40a7f4261bfc2c64bd5ed6dcf7ac28c6e","tid":2361680,"uid":33370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec94ad9107d090c58aa6ff1604e2af8bf7929e4c","tid":2361680,"uid":48026,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3b4bcfc1aff1109192e2f0dfe5d84fa39569ad16","tid":2361680,"uid":235665,"like":9,"dis